- Independent of color changes
- May affect overall mobile layout slightly","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-12T00:40:03.618658128-05:00","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-12T13:20:08.6110451-05:00","closed_at":"2026-01-12T13:20:08.6110451-05:00","close_reason":"Fixed touch target sizes: SpotlightSearch category pills, semantic toggle, mobile close button; BasketSidebar remove button. All now meet 44px minimum. Build passes."}
